title: MsgFileioReadDirResp
description: The read directory message lists the files in a directory on the device's onboard flash file system. Message contains the directory listings as a NULL delimited list. The listing is chunked over multiple SBP packets and the end of the list is identified by an packet with no entries. The sequence number in the response is preserved from the request.
